  "design_note": "The '15' axis is a spatial-weight sweep: 5 core k-aware clusterers (kmeans, gaussian_mixture, agglomerative, spectral, birch) x 3 spatial weights {0.0, 0.3, 0.8}. spatial_weight blends the expression embedding with the spatial-neighbourhood term (0=expression-only, 1=space-only). BANKSY (the one distinct spatial-aware method in the registry) is container/R-only and was not runnable in this environment.",
